-- Central Bank Says China Faces Challenges Meeting Full-Year Lending Target
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-11-24T10:15:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-24/central-bank-says-china-faces-challenges-meeting-full-year-lending-target.html
The People’s Bank of China faces
challenges in meeting its full-year lending target, deputy
Governor Hu Xiaolian said in a statement posted on the bank’s
website today.  China will control the lending pace for the rest of the
year, the statement said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
